description: Preparatory Assistance: Support to Capacity Development of the Judiciary in Zimbabwe

subproject.corporate outcome: Effective, responsive, accessible and fair justice systems promote the rule of law, including both formal and informal processes, with due consideration on the rights of the poor, women and vulnerable groups
subproject.description: The carrying out of a comprehensive capacity assessment to fully ascertain the needs and challenges of the of the judiciary in Zimbabwe and the resultant development of a broad support programme based on the assessment to strengthen the capacity of the judiciary
